READ ME:
To connect the input_event, mouse_entered and mouse_exited signals:
click into entity_placeholder.tscn, 
move to top left menu, click on the node Area3D, 
move to top right, click on "Node" (next to "Inspector"), 
go to "CollisionObject3D", double click on each required signal to connect to the script in the Sprite3D node

https://docs.godotengine.org/en/4.4/getting_started/step_by_step/signals.html
